lemma pnet_init_in_net_tree_ips_in_net_ips [elim]: assumes "s \<in> init (pnet np p)" and "i \<in> net_tree_ips p" shows "i \<in> net_ips s"
proof -
from assms(1)
have "net_ips s = net_tree_ips p"
by (rule pnet_init_net_ips_net_tree_ips)
with \<open>i\<in>net_tree_ips p\<close>
show "i\<in>net_ips s"
by simp
qed
